[0.008, "o", "\u001b[3J\u001b[H\u001b[2J"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[1m   USE CASE — a paid skill marketplace, no human in the loop\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[2.212, "o", "\r\n\r\n\u001b[1;36m▌ 8 · A peer advertises a skill, with a price\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[2.261, "o", "\u001b[0;37m  peer B card:\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[0;37m    skill   compute.run\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[0;37m    price   5 LEZ\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[0;37m    id      Private/6zx8geHx1S3p3sgmMpqBiXM1nq…\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[2.413, "o", "\r\n\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[1;36m▌ 9 · The agent hires it — and pays, by itself\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n"]
[2.250, "o", "\u001b[0;37m  before:  agent 85 LEZ    peer B 0 LEZ\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.212, "o", "\u001b[1m$ logoscore call agent_module agent_task <B-card> compute.run\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.261, "o", "  task task_112775982308666_3 · price 5 · status submitted\r\n"]
[5.032, "o", "  → transfer proof generated\r\n  → transfer proof generated\r\n"]
[3.360, "o", "\u001b[0;37m  after:   agent \u001b[1;32m80\u001b[0m\u001b[0;37m LEZ    peer B \u001b[1;32m5\u001b[0m\u001b[0;37m LEZ\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[0;37m  settled: −5 from the agent's own funds, +5 to the peer\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[2.612, "o", "\r\n\r\n\u001b[1;36m▌ 10 · Over the limit? It asks first\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n"]
[2.215, "o", "\u001b[1m$ agent_task at price 80  (limit is 50)\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.208, "o", "\u001b[0;37m  80 > 50  →  pending_approval\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[0;37m  reason: spend exceeds autonomous threshold — NOT sent\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[2.615, "o", "\r\n\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[1m   Owns its wallet, storage and messaging. Acts on-chain.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[1m   Hires and pays other agents. All under the owner's limits.\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[2.508, "x", "0"]
